#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:2
msgid "系统管理"
msgstr "System Settings"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:4
msgid ""
"本章节介绍系统级通用配置。点击右上角 **齿轮图标** 进入 **设置**，左侧导航栏分为以下主项：**团队**（仅 Admin "
"可见）、**管理模型**、**系统设置**（含 语言、主机、系统配置、全局 OCR "
"模糊映射、捕获模块、模型更新器、编程默认参数、错误类型翻译、标签、校准、关于、日志）以及 **登出**。"
msgstr ""
"This chapter covers system-level configuration. Click the **gear icon** "
"at the top right to open **Settings**. The left navigation is split into:"
" **Team** (Admin only), **Manage Models**, **System Settings** (Language,"
" Host, System Configuration, Global OCR Fuzzy Map, Capture Module, Model "
"Updater, Programming Default Parameters, Error Type Translation, Tags, "
"Calibration, About, Log), and **Log Out**."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:7
msgid "若为首次部署且尚未创建其他账号，请使用部署时提供的 `admin` 初始账号登录完成基础配置。"
msgstr ""
"On a fresh deployment with no other accounts yet, log in with the initial"
" `admin` account provided at deployment time to complete the baseline "
"setup."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:10
msgid "用户与角色权限"
msgstr "Users and roles"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:12
msgid "系统内置三类角色（当前版本账号创建后不支持在界面内修改角色或禁用 / 启用，只能新增与删除）："
msgstr ""
"Three built-in roles ship with the system (the current release does not "
"support changing a role or enabling / disabling an account from the UI — "
"only Create and Delete):"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:14
msgid "角色与权限对照"
msgstr "Roles and permissions"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:18
msgid "角色"
msgstr "Role"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:19
msgid "权限范围"
msgstr "Permissions"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:20
msgid "典型使用场景"
msgstr "Typical use case"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:21
msgid "Admin"
msgstr "Admin"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:22
msgid "全部功能（含成员/角色管理）"
msgstr "Every feature (including member / role management)"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:23
msgid "工程负责人 / 系统管理员"
msgstr "Engineering lead / system administrator"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:24
msgid "编程员"
msgstr "Programmer"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:25
msgid "PCB 产品创建、编程、训练、检测"
msgstr "Create PCB products, program, train, inspect"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:26
msgid "视觉 / 工艺工程师进行模板与参数维护"
msgstr "Vision / process engineers maintaining templates and parameters"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:27
msgid "操作员"
msgstr "Operator"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:28
msgid "仅执行检测任务与缺陷反馈"
msgstr "Run inspection tasks and submit defect feedback only"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:29
msgid "产线操作人员、巡检员"
msgstr "Production-line operator, inspector"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:31
msgid "账号操作（仅 Admin）："
msgstr "Account operations (Admin only):"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:33
msgid "进入：右上角齿轮 → **设置** → 左侧 **团队**。"
msgstr "Open: gear icon → **Settings** → **Team** on the left."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:34
msgid "新增账号：点击\"添加编程人员\"或\"添加操作员\"快捷入口 → 填写 用户名（唯一）/ 初始密码 / 角色 → 保存。"
msgstr ""
"Create an account: click *Add Programmer* or *Add Operator* → fill in a "
"unique username, an initial password, and the role → Save."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:35
msgid "删除账号：在列表对应行点击省略号菜单 → **删除** → 确认。"
msgstr "Delete an account: click the *…* menu on the row → **Delete** → confirm."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:-1
msgid "成员管理界面示意"
msgstr "Member management view"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:46
msgid "操作完成或离开工位时，请立即在\"设置\"中登出，防止他人误用会话。"
msgstr ""
"When you finish or leave the workstation, log out from **Settings** right"
" away so the session can't be misused."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:49
msgid "多语言设置"
msgstr "Language"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:51
msgid "系统支持界面多语言（当前已支持：中文 / English）。多语言切换只影响 UI 字符串，不改变已创建的 PCB 产品名称与元件标识。"
msgstr ""
"The UI supports multiple languages (currently Chinese / English). "
"Language switching only changes UI strings — existing PCB product names "
"and component designators are unaffected."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:53
#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:78
msgid "切换步骤："
msgstr "Steps:"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:55
msgid "登录后点击右上角齿轮进入 **设置**。"
msgstr "After login, click the gear icon at the top right to open **Settings**."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:56
msgid "在左侧 **系统设置** → **语言** 中找到\"系统语言\"。"
msgstr ""
"On the left, go to **System Settings → Language** to find *System "
"language*."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:57
msgid "下拉选择目标语言（中文 / English）后，界面自动应用。"
msgstr ""
"Pick the target language (Chinese / English) from the drop-down; the UI "
"applies it immediately."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:-1
msgid "切换语言示意"
msgstr "Language switching"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:64
msgid "语言切换不会重启后端；若浏览器多标签页打开本系统，请全部刷新以保持一致。"
msgstr ""
"Language switching does not restart the backend; if the system is open in"
" multiple browser tabs, refresh them all to keep them in sync."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:67
msgid "后端地址管理"
msgstr "Host management"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:69
msgid "用于让当前浏览器前端连接指定的后端服务实例，并在多个部署环境（本地 / 测试 / 生产 / 备用节点）之间快速切换。"
msgstr ""
"Lets the browser frontend connect to a specific backend instance and "
"switch quickly among deployment environments — local, staging, "
"production, fallback node."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:71
msgid "常见使用场景："
msgstr "Common use cases:"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:73
msgid "产线上使用笔记本或平板（Wi‑Fi）直接访问机台后端，无需占用后端主机显示器。"
msgstr ""
"On the line, use a laptop or tablet over Wi-Fi to talk to the machine's "
"backend without occupying the host's monitor."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:74
msgid "质检 / 工程 人员可在不同工位快速切换到测试或生产环境查看训练 / 检测状态。"
msgstr ""
"QA / engineering staff can hop between workstations and switch quickly "
"between staging and production to check training / inspection status."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:75
msgid "支持远程协助：暂时指向测试服务器复现问题，再切回生产。"
msgstr ""
"Supports remote assistance: point temporarily at the staging server to "
"reproduce a problem, then switch back to production."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:76
msgid "集中管理：同一前端界面可按需切换不同产线后端，统一查看检测结果、启动训练或执行任务，无需分别登录多台主机。"
msgstr ""
"Centralized management: the same frontend can switch between line-side "
"backends on demand — view inspection results, start training, or run "
"tasks — without logging into each host separately."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:80
msgid "点击右上角齿轮 → **设置**，在左侧选择 **系统设置** → **主机**。"
msgstr ""
"Click the gear icon → **Settings**, then pick **System Settings → Host** "
"on the left."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:81
msgid ""
"在\"当前主机\"输入框中查看 / 修改后端地址（默认为 `localhost:8000`）；可通过协议前缀下拉框选择 `http://` 或 "
"`https://`。"
msgstr ""
"The *Current host* input shows or edits the backend address (defaults to "
"`localhost:8000`). The protocol drop-down toggles between `http://` and "
"`https://`."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:82
msgid "输入新的服务地址（含端口，如 `10.0.0.12:8000`）。"
msgstr "Type the new address (including the port, e.g. `10.0.0.12:8000`)."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:83
msgid "点击\"保存\"，页面自动重新连接。"
msgstr "Click **Save**; the page reconnects automatically."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:-1
msgid "后端地址切换示意"
msgstr "Host switching"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:93
msgid "系统配置"
msgstr "System Configuration"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:95
msgid "进入路径：右上角齿轮 → **设置** → **系统设置** → **系统配置**。"
msgstr "Open: gear icon → **Settings → System Settings → System Configuration**."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:97
msgid "页面标题为\"编辑系统配置\"，包含以下几个配置区块（Admin / 编程员 可见）："
msgstr ""
"The page is titled *Edit System Configuration* and contains the following"
" blocks (visible to Admin and Programmer):"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:-1
msgid "系统配置界面示意"
msgstr "System Configuration view"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:103
msgid "**MES导出配置**"
msgstr "**MES Export configuration**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:105
msgid "用于配置将检测结果导出至 MES 系统的行为。"
msgstr "Configures how inspection results are exported to a MES system."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:107
msgid "MES 导出选项说明"
msgstr "MES export options"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:111
#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:144
msgid "选项"
msgstr "Option"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:112
#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:145
#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:210
#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:231
#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:256
#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:287
#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:330
msgid "说明"
msgstr "Description"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:113
msgid "值"
msgstr "Value"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:114
msgid "导出MES路径"
msgstr "Export MES Path"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:115
msgid "用于保存导出的 MES 文件与相关资源；请确保目标目录存在且有写入权限。"
msgstr ""
"Where the exported MES files and related artifacts are saved. Make sure "
"the target directory exists and is writable."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:116
msgid "导出路径的绝对地址"
msgstr "Absolute path"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:117
msgid "导出报告"
msgstr "Export Report"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:118
msgid "导出包含检测概览、统计与缺陷摘要的报告文件，便于对外流转与存档。"
msgstr ""
"Export a report file containing the inspection overview, statistics, and "
"a defect summary — useful for handoff and archival."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:119
#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:122
#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:125
#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:158
#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:260
#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:263
#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:266
#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:291
#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:294
#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:297
msgid "开启/关闭"
msgstr "On / Off"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:120
msgid "导出元件图像"
msgstr "Export Component Image"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:121
msgid "针对每个缺陷元件导出裁剪的局部图像，便于 MES 或质检系统联动查看细节。"
msgstr ""
"For each defective component, export a cropped local image so MES or "
"downstream QA systems can view the detail."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:123
msgid "导出拼接图像"
msgstr "Export Stitched Image"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:124
msgid "导出整板拼接大图，用于复核现场光照、对齐与整体检测效果。"
msgstr ""
"Export the stitched whole-board image to review on-site lighting, "
"alignment, and overall inspection quality."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:126
msgid "导出图像质量（1-100）"
msgstr "Export Image Quality (1–100)"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:127
msgid "控制导出 JPEG 等有损格式的压缩质量；数值越大图像越清晰、文件体积越大。"
msgstr ""
"Controls JPEG / other lossy-format quality on export; higher values are "
"sharper but larger."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:128
msgid "1–100"
msgstr "1–100"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:129
msgid "报告保存期限（1-30天）"
msgstr "Report Retention (1–30 days)"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:130
msgid "在导出目录中为报告与图像设置保留天数；超过期限的历史文件可由系统定期清理，节省空间。"
msgstr ""
"Retention period for reports and images in the export directory; expired "
"files are cleaned up by the periodic sweep to free space."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:131
msgid "1–30 天"
msgstr "1–30 days"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:134
msgid "导出配置文件的选择、默认 ``default_csv`` 配置的存图路径与报告字段说明，详见 :ref:`MES 结果导出`。"
msgstr ""
"For choosing an export profile and the image storage paths and report "
"fields of the default ``default_csv`` profile, see :ref:`MES 结果导出`."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:136
msgid "**检测记录**"
msgstr "**Inspection records**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:138
msgid "管理检测结果数据的保留与清理策略。"
msgstr "Manages the retention and cleanup policy for inspection-result data."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:140
msgid "检测记录选项说明"
msgstr "Inspection-record options"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:146
msgid "值/示例"
msgstr "Value / example"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:147
msgid "检测结果保留天数"
msgstr "Inspection-result retention days"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:148
msgid "超过此天数的历史检测结果将在定时清理时被删除。"
msgstr ""
"Historical inspection results older than this are deleted by the "
"scheduled cleanup."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:149
msgid "天数（默认 90）"
msgstr "Days (default 90)"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:150
msgid "磁盘空间不足警告阈值（GiB）"
msgstr "Disk-space warning threshold (GiB)"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:151
msgid "剩余磁盘空间低于此值时系统启动警告；设为 0 可禁用。"
msgstr ""
"The system warns when free disk space drops below this value; set to 0 to"
" disable."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:152
msgid "GiB（默认 30）"
msgstr "GiB (default 30)"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:153
msgid "大文件存储位置"
msgstr "Large-file storage location"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:154
msgid "检测图像等大文件的存储卷；若默认盘空间不足可切换至其他卷，修改后需重启生效。"
msgstr ""
"The volume that stores large files such as inspection images. Switch to "
"another volume if the default drive is short on space; restart for the "
"change to take effect."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:155
msgid "目录路径（留空为默认）"
msgstr "Directory path (empty = default)"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:156
msgid "定时清理"
msgstr "Scheduled cleanup"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:157
msgid "启用后，系统将在指定时间自动清理超期检测记录。"
msgstr ""
"When enabled, the system runs the cleanup at the configured time and "
"removes expired records."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:159
msgid "定时清理时间"
msgstr "Scheduled cleanup time"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:160
msgid "定时清理任务的执行时刻（格式 HH:MM，24 小时制）。"
msgstr "Time the scheduled cleanup runs (HH:MM, 24-hour)."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:161
msgid "如 ``01:00``"
msgstr "e.g. ``01:00``"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:162
msgid "立即清除检测记录"
msgstr "Cleanup Records Now"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:163
msgid "点击后立即触发清理任务，将超过保留天数的检测记录删除。适用于需要快速释放磁盘空间的场景。"
msgstr ""
"Clicking it kicks off the cleanup immediately, deleting records past the "
"retention period — useful when you need to free disk space quickly."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:164
msgid "按钮"
msgstr "Button"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:166
msgid "**合格结果二次确认**"
msgstr "**Pass-result secondary confirmation**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:168
msgid "启用后，实时检测页面检测到合格（OK）时弹出确认窗口，由操作员手动判定合格或不合格。"
msgstr ""
"When enabled, every Pass (OK) verdict on the Live page surfaces a "
"confirmation dialog so the operator can confirm Pass or override to NG."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:172
msgid "全局 OCR 模糊字符映射"
msgstr "Global OCR Fuzzy Character Map"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:174
msgid "进入路径：右上角齿轮 → **设置** → **系统设置** → **全局 OCR 模糊映射** \\ （Admin / 编程员 可见）。"
msgstr ""
"Open: gear icon → **Settings → System Settings → Global OCR Fuzzy Map** "
"(visible to Admin and Programmer)."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:176
msgid ""
"页面标题为\"全局 OCR 模糊字符映射\"。这里维护一份全线统一的字符等价表，供 **文本检测（OCR）** 的模糊匹配使用：同一分组内的字符在"
" OCR 文本校验时视为可互换（例如 ``O`` / ``0`` / ``Q``）。每个分组需包含 **3 个或更多** "
"字符，该表对所有启用了模糊匹配的产品生效。"
msgstr ""
"The page is titled \"Global OCR Fuzzy Character Map\". It maintains a "
"single line-wide table of character equivalences used by **Text (OCR)** "
"fuzzy matching: characters in the same group are treated as "
"interchangeable during OCR text verification (e.g. ``O`` / ``0`` / "
"``Q``). Each group must contain **3 or more** characters, and the table "
"applies to all products where fuzzy matching is enabled."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:178
#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:390
msgid "操作说明："
msgstr "How to use:"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:180
msgid "**添加分组**：新增一个等价分组。"
msgstr "**Add group**: add a new equivalence group."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:181
msgid ""
"在分组内点击 **+ 字符** 添加成员；每个成员只能是 **单个** 大写字母或数字（``A``–``Z`` / "
"``0``–``9``），输入会自动转为大写。"
msgstr ""
"Inside a group, click **+ Character** to add a member; each member must "
"be a **single** uppercase letter or digit (``A``–``Z`` / ``0``–``9``), "
"and the input is automatically converted to uppercase."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:182
msgid "**删除分组**：移除整个分组。"
msgstr "**Remove group**: remove the whole group."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:183
msgid ""
"编辑完成后点击 **保存全局映射**。保存成功提示\"全局 OCR 模糊映射已保存\"，失败提示\"保存全局 OCR 模糊映射失败\"。保存时少于"
" 2 个成员的分组会被自动丢弃。"
msgstr ""
"When you are done editing, click **Save Global Map**. Success shows "
"\"Global OCR fuzzy map saved\" and failure shows \"Failed to save global "
"OCR fuzzy map\". Groups with fewer than 2 members are dropped "
"automatically on save."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:186
msgid ""
"过宽的分组（例如 ``8`` ↔ "
"``B``）会使该混淆在全线所有文本元件上都被接受，从而在各处屏蔽此类缺陷。请保持全局映射的保守；针对特定料号的情况，请改用文本检测页 "
":ref:`文本检测（Text / OCR · OCV）` 的 **模糊模式（Blur Mode）** 按元件学习。"
msgstr ""
"A broad group (e.g. ``8`` ↔ ``B``) makes that confusion acceptable on "
"every text feature line-wide, suppressing those defects everywhere. Keep "
"the global map conservative; for part-specific cases, use per-component "
"learning via **Blur Mode** on the text inspection page instead (see "
":ref:`文本检测（Text / OCR · OCV）`)."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:189
msgid "修改后在 **下一次检测会话启动时生效**，无需重启后端；正在运行的会话不会立即更新。"
msgstr ""
"Changes take effect **at the start of the next inspection session**; no "
"backend restart is needed, and a session that is already running is not "
"updated immediately."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:-1
msgid "全局 OCR 模糊字符映射 编辑页面：分组列表与 添加分组 / 保存全局映射 按钮"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:197
