msgid "基线曝光时间（单位因硬件而异）；现场光照稳定后再调整。"
msgstr ""
"Baseline exposure time (units depend on the hardware). Tune only after "
"on-site lighting is stable."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:241
msgid "模型更新器"
msgstr "Model Updater"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:243
msgid "进入路径：右上角齿轮 → **设置** → **系统设置** → **模型更新器**。"
msgstr "Open: gear icon → **Settings → System Settings → Model Updater**."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:245
msgid ""
"页面标题为\"模型更新器配置\"（Admin / 编程员 "
"可见），用于在运行过程中根据现场图像统计自动或半自动更新各检测模块的颜色阈值与比例参数，以提升 2D 焊点 / "
"引脚等检测的稳健性。修改后保存并自动重载页面。"
msgstr ""
"The page is titled *Model Updater Configuration* (visible to Admin and "
"Programmer). It updates the color thresholds and ratio parameters of each"
" inspection module automatically — or semi-automatically — based on on-"
"site image statistics, to improve robustness on 2D solder / lead "
"inspections. Saving reloads the page automatically."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:247
msgid "配置存储在 ``model_updater_config.json``。"
msgstr "The configuration is persisted to ``model_updater_config.json``."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:249
msgid "**焊接 2D（solder_2d）**"
msgstr "**Solder 2D (``solder_2d``)**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:251
