#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:296
msgid "是否允许 AI 模型的更新结果覆盖本地统计参数。"
msgstr ""
"Whether AI-model update results can override the local statistical "
"parameters."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:267
msgid "红色比例最小值（red_ratio_min）"
msgstr "Red Ratio Min (``red_ratio_min``)"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:268
msgid "红色通道占比下限，用于限定有效焊点颜色特征范围。"
msgstr ""
"Lower bound for the red-channel ratio, used to constrain the valid "
"solder-joint color range."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:269
msgid "0–100（默认 0）"
msgstr "0–100 (default 0)"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:270
msgid "红色比例最大值（red_ratio_max）"
msgstr "Red Ratio Max (``red_ratio_max``)"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:271
msgid "红色通道占比上限。"
msgstr "Upper bound for the red-channel ratio."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:272
msgid "0–100（默认 50）"
msgstr "0–100 (default 50)"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:273
msgid "非红色比例最小值（non_red_ratio_min）"
msgstr "Non-Red Ratio Min (``non_red_ratio_min``)"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:274
msgid "非红色通道占比下限；与红色比例共同约束目标的颜色分布，避免误检。"
msgstr ""
"Lower bound for the non-red ratio; together with the red ratio, "
"constrains the target color distribution and reduces false positives."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:275
#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:300
msgid "0–100（默认 20）"
msgstr "0–100 (default 20)"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:276
msgid "非红色比例最大值（non_red_ratio_max）"
msgstr "Non-Red Ratio Max (``non_red_ratio_max``)"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:277
msgid "非红色通道占比上限。"
msgstr "Upper bound for the non-red ratio."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:278
#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:303
msgid "0–100（默认 100）"
msgstr "0–100 (default 100)"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:280
msgid "**引脚 2D V2（lead_2d_v2）**"
msgstr "**Lead 2D V2 (``lead_2d_v2``)**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:282
msgid "lead_2d_v2 关键字段"
msgstr "``lead_2d_v2`` key fields"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:290
msgid "是否允许自动调整引脚区域的颜色范围阈值。"
msgstr ""
"Whether the color-range threshold for the lead region can be auto-"
"adjusted."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:293
msgid "是否允许更新引脚颜色比例阈值。"
msgstr "Whether the lead color-ratio threshold can be updated."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:298
msgid "焊接比例最小值（solder_ratio_min）"
msgstr "Solder Ratio Min (``solder_ratio_min``)"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:299
msgid "引脚焊接区域颜色比例下限。"
msgstr "Lower bound for the lead solder region's color ratio."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:301
msgid "焊接比例最大值（solder_ratio_max）"
msgstr "Solder Ratio Max (``solder_ratio_max``)"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:302
msgid "引脚焊接区域颜色比例上限。"
msgstr "Upper bound for the lead solder region's color ratio."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:306
msgid "开启自动更新（更新颜色范围 / 更新颜色比例）后，请在稳定的光照与工艺条件下运行一段时间以收集统计，避免短期波动导致参数过度调整。"
msgstr ""
"After enabling auto-update (**Update Color Range** / **Update Color "
"Ratio**), run for a while under stable lighting and process conditions so"
" statistics can accumulate; otherwise short-term fluctuations may swing "
"the parameters too far."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:307
msgid "建议结合版本管理或备份原始配置文件，必要时可回滚到上一版本参数集。"
msgstr ""
"Pair this with version control or back up the original configuration file"
" so you can roll back to an earlier parameter set if needed."

