"(``wasted_array_board_failure_ratio``) is now configured per product "
"under **Teach → Recipe → Inspection Settings** and is no longer shown "
"here."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:349
msgid "错误类型翻译"
msgstr "Error Type Translation"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:351
msgid "进入路径：右上角齿轮 → **设置** → **系统设置** → **错误类型翻译** \\ （Admin / 编程员 可见）。"
msgstr ""
"Open: gear icon → **Settings → System Settings → Error Type Translation**"
" (visible to Admin and Programmer)."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:-1
