msgstr "Tag Management"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:380
msgid "进入路径：右上角齿轮 → **设置** → **系统设置** → **标签** \\ （Admin / 编程员 可见）。"
msgstr ""
"Open: gear icon → **Settings → System Settings → Tags** (visible to Admin"
" and Programmer)."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:382
msgid ""
"标签（Tags）是附加到 PCB "
"产品程序上的自定义分类标记，用于在产品列表和检测任务启动时快速筛选产品。标签一旦绑定到至少一个程序后即出现在此页面。"
msgstr ""
"Tags are user-defined labels attached to PCB product programs; they speed"
" up filtering on the product list and during inspection-task setup. A tag"
" appears on this page once it is bound to at least one program."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:384
msgid "页面包含以下列："
msgstr "Columns:"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:386
msgid "**名称**：标签的文本内容。"
msgstr "**Name**: the tag's text."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:387
msgid "**产品数**：使用该标签的产品数量（只读）。"
msgstr "**Product count**: number of products using this tag (read-only)."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:388
msgid "**操作**：**重命名** / **删除** 按钮。"
msgstr "**Actions**: **Rename** / **Delete** buttons."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:392
msgid "**重命名**：点击\"重命名\"按钮，在弹窗中输入新名称后确认；重命名将同步应用到该标签下的所有产品。若新名称与已有标签冲突将提示错误。"
msgstr ""
"**Rename**: click *Rename*, type the new name in the dialog, and confirm;"
" the rename applies to every product carrying the tag. A collision with "
"an existing tag triggers an error."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:393
msgid "**删除**：点击\"删除\"按钮，确认后该标签将从所有已绑定产品中移除。"
msgstr ""
"**Delete**: click *Delete* and confirm; the tag is removed from every "
"product currently carrying it."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:396
msgid "在产品列表（首页）选中产品后可批量添加或移除标签；在编辑产品信息时也可为单个产品管理标签。"
msgstr ""
"From the product list on the home page, select products to batch-add or "
"batch-remove tags; tags can also be managed per product via *Edit Info*."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:400
msgid "相机现场校准"
msgstr "On-site camera calibration"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:402
msgid "用于在线更新相机的内参 / 畸变参数，确保尺寸测量及对齐精度。当出现以下任一情况，建议执行一次现场校准："
msgstr ""
"Updates the camera's intrinsic and distortion parameters in the field to "
"keep dimensional measurement and alignment accurate. Run an on-site "
"calibration when any of the following apply:"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:404
msgid "更换或重新安装相机 / 镜头；"
msgstr "The camera or lens was replaced or reinstalled."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:405
msgid "调整过镜头焦距或光圈，导致成像比例明显变化；"
msgstr ""
"The lens focal length or aperture was changed, producing a visibly "
"different imaging scale."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:406
msgid "相机支撑结构被移动、震动或维护后位置可能偏移；"
msgstr "The camera mount was moved, knocked, or serviced and may have shifted."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:407
msgid "图像边缘出现明显拉伸 / 弯曲，或测量尺寸偏差增大；"
msgstr ""
"The image edges show visible stretch or curvature, or measured dimensions"
" drift more than usual."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:408
msgid "模板匹配稳定性下降（需先排除光照与污渍因素）。"
msgstr ""
"Template-matching stability has dropped (rule out lighting and "
"contamination first)."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:411
msgid "校准操作会更新当前使用的标定文件（`certificate.bin`）。若需保留旧版本，可在执行前手动备份原文件。"
msgstr ""
"Calibration updates the active calibration file (`certificate.bin`). Back"
" up the original by hand before running it if you want to keep the "
"previous version."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:413
msgid "前提准备："
msgstr "Prerequisites:"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:415
msgid "使用官方提供的标定板（保持清洁、无划痕、无强反光）；"
msgstr ""
"Use the official calibration target (keep it clean, scratch-free, and "
"free of strong reflections)."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:416
msgid "确保现场光照稳定，避免强烈局部反射；"
msgstr "Ensure on-site lighting is stable and free of strong local reflections."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:417
msgid "传送带参数（宽度 / 速度）已正确配置。"
msgstr "Conveyor parameters (width / speed) are configured correctly."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:419
#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:496
msgid "操作步骤："
msgstr "Steps:"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:-1
msgid "相机现场校准示意"
msgstr "On-site camera calibration"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:425
msgid "打开：右上角齿轮 → **设置** → **系统设置** → **校准**。"
msgstr "Open: gear icon → **Settings → System Settings → Calibration**."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:426
msgid "将标定板放置在传送带中央，棋盘格（或圆点阵）面朝上，整体尽量覆盖相机主要视野；保持平整、不倾斜。"
msgstr ""
"Place the calibration target flat in the center of the conveyor, "
"checkerboard (or dot pattern) facing up, covering as much of the camera's"
" primary field of view as possible; keep it level — no tilt."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:427
msgid "点击\"开始校准\"。系统将自动执行：进板 → 拍照采集 → 出板。"
msgstr ""
"Click **Start Calibration**. The system automatically runs PCB In → "
"capture → PCB Out."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:428
msgid "采集完成后前端显示进度与结果状态；成功时出现\"校准成功\"提示。"
msgstr ""
"When capture finishes, the frontend shows progress and result status; a "
"*Calibration successful* prompt appears on success."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:429
msgid "校准文件 `certificate.bin` 自动更新；可记录时间戳以便追溯。"
msgstr ""
"The calibration file `certificate.bin` is updated automatically; record "
"the timestamp for traceability if you want."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:433
msgid "校准过程中勿触碰标定板或传送带，避免产生运动模糊导致参数偏差。"
msgstr ""
"Do not touch the target or the conveyor during calibration — motion blur "
"will throw off the parameters."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:437
msgid "关于"
msgstr "About"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:439
msgid "进入路径：右上角齿轮 → **设置** → **系统设置** → **关于**。"
msgstr "Open: gear icon → **Settings → System Settings → About**."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:441
msgid "在该页面可以查询以下信息："
msgstr "This page lists:"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:443
msgid "**版本**：当前后端系统版本号。"
msgstr "**Version**: the current backend system version."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:444
msgid "**加密密钥ID**：系统授权加密密钥标识符。"
msgstr "**Dongle ID**: the system's licence-dongle identifier."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:445
msgid "**加密有效期至** \\ （若存在）：授权到期日期；若已过期请联系技术支持更新授权。"
msgstr ""
"**Licence expiry** (when present): the licence end date. If it has "
"expired, contact technical support to renew."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:449
msgid "日志"
msgstr "Log"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:451
msgid "进入路径：右上角齿轮 → **设置** → **系统设置** → **日志**。"
msgstr "Open: gear icon → **Settings → System Settings → Log**."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:-1
msgid "系统日志界面示意"
msgstr "System Log view"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:457
msgid "**输出日志详细程度（log verbosity）**"
msgstr "**Log verbosity**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:459
msgid "页面提供一个数字输入框，取值范围 **0–10 的整数**："
msgstr "The page offers a numeric input that accepts **integers 0–10**:"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:461
msgid "**0**：仅输出错误与启动 / 关闭信息（最简）。"
msgstr "**0**: errors plus start / stop messages only — quietest."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:462
msgid "**3–5**：常规生产环境推荐值，仅记录关键流程与必要诊断信息。"
msgstr ""
"**3–5**: recommended for production — logs the critical flow and the "
"diagnostics actually needed."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:463
msgid "**8–10**：调试 / 排查问题时使用；记录每次检测的详细推理过程与中间数据。"
msgstr ""
"**8–10**: for debugging and troubleshooting — logs every inspection's "
"detailed inference flow and intermediate data."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:465
msgid "调整后点击 **应用** 按钮立即生效，无需重启后端服务；当前值由后端持久保存，重启后保留。"
msgstr ""
"Click **Apply** after editing; the change takes effect immediately, no "
"backend restart required. The current value is persisted on the backend "
"and survives a restart."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:469
msgid ""
"将日志详细程度调到较高值（约 8–10）会显著增加每次检测的耗时（约 100–200 "
"毫秒每板），并占用更多磁盘空间。建议平时保持较低值，仅在排查问题时临时调高，问题定位完成后再调回。"
msgstr ""
"Raising log verbosity to a high value (around 8–10) significantly "
"increases per-board inspection time (roughly 100–200 ms per board) and "
"disk usage. Keep verbosity low day-to-day and only raise it temporarily "
"for troubleshooting, then drop it back."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:473
msgid "管理模型"
msgstr "Manage Models"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:475
msgid ""
"**设置** 左侧的 **管理模型** 用于查看系统中的检测模型（按 全部 / 预训练 / 已训练 "
"筛选），并支持上传模型、训练模型、设为默认、重命名、导出与删除，以及数据集的导出 / 导入和训练预热重置等操作。模型训练、数据集导入 / "
"导出等完整流程详见 :ref:`模型管理` 章节。"
msgstr ""
"**Manage Models** on the left of **Settings** lists the inspection models"
" in the system (filterable by All / Pre-trained / Trained), and supports "
"Upload, Train, Set as Default, Rename, Export, and Delete, along with "
"dataset Export / Import and training-warmup reset. The full reference for"
" training and dataset operations lives in :ref:`模型管理`."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:479
msgid "数据备份和迁移"
msgstr "Data backup and migration"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:481
msgid "随着检测记录不断积累，硬盘空间会逐渐减少，建议定期进行数据备份和清理。"
msgstr ""
"As inspection records pile up, disk space dwindles — back up and clean up"
" data periodically."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:483
msgid "请在安装目录下运行 `aoi_pcb_blob_liner.exe` 工具。"
msgstr "Run `aoi_pcb_blob_liner.exe` from the install directory."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:485
msgid "主要界面说明（见下图）："
msgstr "Main UI (see below):"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:-1
msgid "数据迁移示意"
msgstr "Data migration"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:491
msgid "左上角 File → FTP mount points 可配置 FTP 服务器，实现远程备份到 NAS 或其他网络硬盘。"
msgstr ""
"Top-left **File → FTP mount points** configures an FTP server for remote "
"backup to a NAS or other network drive."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:492
msgid "右上角 Destination Volume 用于选择目标盘（如移动硬盘、第二磁盘等）。"
msgstr ""
"**Destination Volume** at the top-right picks the target drive (an "
"external drive, a second internal disk, and so on)."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:493
msgid "上方搜索栏可按产品名或序列号快速检索检测记录。"
msgstr ""
"The search bar at the top filters inspection records by product name or "
"serial number."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:494
msgid "搜索栏旁边的过滤器按钮可按日期、时间等条件过滤记录，便于批量操作。"
msgstr ""
"The filter button next to the search bar filters by date / time so batch "
"operations are easier."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:498
msgid "选择目标盘（Destination Volume），如需远程备份可先配置 FTP。"
msgstr ""
"Pick the **Destination Volume**; configure FTP first if you need remote "
"backup."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:499
msgid "可通过搜索栏输入产品名或序列号，或点击 过滤器 按钮按日期/时间筛选需要迁移的检测记录。"
msgstr ""
"Filter the records to migrate by typing a product name or serial number "
"in the search bar, or by clicking the filter button to filter by date / "
"time."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:500
msgid "在列表中框选或按住 Shift 选中多个检测记录。"
msgstr "Drag-select or Shift-click to pick multiple records in the list."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:501
msgid "点击下方 Archive 按钮，即可将选中的记录迁移至目标盘。"
msgstr ""
"Click the **Archive** button at the bottom to migrate the selected "
"records to the destination drive."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:502
msgid "如需恢复数据，可点击 Unarchive 按钮从目标盘导入。"
msgstr "Click **Unarchive** to restore data from the destination drive."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:503
msgid "若需删除无用记录，可点击 Delete 按钮。"
msgstr "Click **Delete** to remove unwanted records."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:-1
msgid "目标磁盘中的归档文件示意"
msgstr "Archive files on the destination drive"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/system_management/index.rst:509
msgid "建议定期将重要检测数据备份到安全存储介质，防止因硬盘故障或空间不足导致数据丢失。"
msgstr ""
"Back up critical inspection data to safe storage periodically so a disk "
"failure or space shortage doesn't lose it."

